announced, only for it later to be revealed that it was all one big mistake.

00:00:55.502 --> 00:01:00.342
OK then, let’s not waste a minute, and talk about Bad Science.

00:01:02.242 --> 00:01:08.972
You may know that the most popular British newspaper by practically every metric is The Daily Mail.

00:01:09.782 --> 00:01:13.692
It boasts a couple of million daily readers of its physical

00:01:13.692 --> 00:01:16.890
newspapers, swelling to three million on the weekend.

